body:
Here are some Dan and Phil moodboards I made today~ I’ll give you a quick run over each one~

The first moodboard: this moodboard is a Phan one, and is themed around rain, the beach, darkness, nearing nighttime, sleep, love, kisses, romance, and relaxation~ 🖤🌊🌧🛌

The second moodboard: this is yet another Phan moodboard, which is also centered around comfort, confidence, reassurance, being there for one another, recovery, rainbows, strength, gay love, and resilience~ 🌈❤️🧡💛💚💙💜

The third moodboard: this is a Phil moodboard, based on pastel colours ( lavender and lilac ), respect, acceptance, happiness, diversity, uniqueness, and self/general love~ 🌸🍬💿👚🥣


Hope u like these~ (//∇//) ✿
